 @Matt M  I agree as time progresses more and more will resist or speak up.  These are those that final had enough, have witnessed others blaze the trail before and have spoken up now as they feel there is less risk.
My question would be, what do you think it would take to get the bulk of the status quo crowd to abandon their cultist mind frame and feel empowered and secure enough to actually resist authority and speak truth to power?
I take comfort in seeing more and more of those who find themselves on the right finally begin to question their loyalty to cops for example.  This is a healthy sign in my estimation.  But what would it take for the bulk to begin resisting?

 @Jonathan Ward  If someone has never watched one of his videos before, they might easily assume he'll be off-topic  for most of the video.

There are so many videos where other creators fluff a 5 second news bit into 10 minutes (or more).

You and I know Viva will deliver the goods...which is why we are patient.
